title: Don't match on username in the message, only look at text
Explicitly direct people to chat channels
body: A number of people have started using channel names as hashtags on the mailing lists. I want to make it obvious it is an actual chat channel, not a hashtag.

title: added Josh Smith as an expert
Change pattern for testing
